Package Utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DriverManager
    This class manages the driver, has all the actions and screenshots methods
    Execute
    This class iterates each of the steps in the list we receive from readxmls and sends them to the driver manager for execution in addition to creating and opening reports.
    OpenHtml
    this class opens the test reports file
    ReadXmls
    This class returns a list of steps list read from the excel file.
    ReportMaker
    in this class an html file is created
    Step
    In this class there are all the characteristics of an step
    WiniumManager
    This class handles winium drivers to be able to select a photo. for the edit profile and project creation stories.
